          <![CDATA[Paul Chung]]>
        </name>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[Viewpoint and Thailand Holiday Homes = WIN

Paul at Thailand Holiday Homes made my enquiry easy and assisting with organizing 3 villas in close quarters to each other for a party of 16 in Viewpoint Village Jomtien.

Everything prior to arriving was very smooth and made easy. He advised us of one original villa becoming unavailable and promptly organized a new one for us in the same location.

Transfers were also organized through Paul which was pleasant for a group of 16 tired travellers.

On arrival, Tuk showed us all 3 properties, and was very thorough in providing contact details if we needed assistance with anything, left business cards for taxi drivers to find our location easily (this came handy countless times in our 4 night stay), as well as advising us of policies and checking electricity meters. She also helped organize scooters which of course are always a convenient way of getting around.

All three residences were comfortable and after staying in hotels we felt at home very easily and quickly. Everything was in working order and the pools were a lazy way of having a morning or evening dip.

Convenience stores and local restaurants location nearby, Viewpoint were a short distance from Jomtien beach, and a brief drive to Pattaya Walking Street. After a day, we were glad to be distant from Walking Street as our surroundings in Viewpoint were peaceful and convenient in its own way.

Thanks to Thailand Holiday Homes for making our stay pleasant and would definitely consider another stay with Paul and his crew, hopefully for a longer period next time.]]>
